Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:36.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}思いを重ねた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:43.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}祈りは時を超えて
