Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:55.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}至少纵声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:22:07.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恸哭和绝望之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:12.85,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}等待我们的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:20.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}都不过是生命梦想的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:23.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为之奋斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.36,0:22:28.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}当下的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:34.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你哭泣的夜晚之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:40.88,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}藏有遥远未来的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.13,0:22:45.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}静谧在等待你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:51.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}耀眼的丘陵 必能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.93,0:22:57.35,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你所在的地平线
